 ./modules/control/rc/rc.c: fixed a segfault when pressing 'i' with no
 input

2002-08-13 Tuesday 13:59  sam

   * ./modules/audio_output/oss.c: we spare a variable by using p_aout->b_die
     instead of our own variable.
