2002-03-17 Sunday 18:00  sam

   * ./plugins/chroma/i420_rgb8.c: plain C 8 bpp transformation.
   * ./plugins/chroma/i420_rgb16.c: plain C 24/32 bpp transformations.
   * ./plugins/ggi/ggi.c: support for 8 bpp displays.
