  . no need to add "\n" at the end of intf_*Msg() messages anymore.

2000-12-22 Friday 11:58  massiot

 * Moved input_DecodePES() to input_dec.c ;
 * Fixed an segfault in input_programs.c ;
 * Added -fomit-frame-pointer optimization.

